elements.2211.03093_8d16f583a0e1d08fb6c5460030958: Positioning with one inertial measurement unit and one ranging sensor is commonly thought to be feasible only when trajectories are in certain patterns ensuring observability
elements.2211.03093_eb0c7f38bdc169b1ad97bbb934ad2: For this reason, to pursue observable patterns, it is required either exciting the trajectory or searching key nodes in a long interval, which is commonly highly nonlinear and may also lack resilience
elements.2211.03093_c8f62134bdf308a427cb8844b77d5: Therefore, such a positioning approach is still not widely accepted in real-world applications
elements.2211.03093_a040586f4230c2437b88ebbd12409: To address this issue, this work first investigates the dissipative nature of flying robots considering aerial drag effects and re-formulates the corresponding positioning problem, which guarantees observability almost surely
elements.2211.03093_7ba3fd6a3a99ba3cfe31e99f7898c: On this basis, a dimension-reduced wriggling estimator is proposed accordingly
elements.2211.03093_1072dbe8723eb79b3e9ca35d4c565: This estimator slides the estimation horizon in a stepping manner, and output matrices can be approximately evaluated based on the historical estimation sequence
elements.2211.03093_15b4b9b7dd514be483037c51d418d: The computational complexity is then further reduced via a dimension-reduction approach using polynomial fittings
elements.2211.03093_56e33aa4e155daab7c21a196bf522: In this way, the states of robots can be estimated via linear programming in a sufficiently long interval, and the degree of observability is thereby further enhanced because an adequate redundancy of measurements is available for each estimation
elements.2211.03093_a4eb263aeb776c346fc2d94c3d5db: Subsequently, the estimator's convergence and numerical stability are proven theoretically
elements.2211.03093_bf82c23891804502a5ae092429dc0: Finally, both indoor and outdoor experiments verify that the proposed estimator can achieve decimeter-level precision at hundreds of hertz per second, and it is resilient to sensors' failures
elements.2211.03093_41e4713213f4928a42a9db171ef93: Hopefully, this study can provide a new practical approach for self-localization as well as relative positioning of cooperative agents with low-cost and lightweight sensors.
elements.2211.03093_b749faf42f6cae034d7a9dd83a8da: Sing Range, Observability, Dimension-reduced Wriggling Estimator, Dissipative, Aerial Drag
elements.2211.03093_ac9151b51b4324f0e309aba46cfaf: Inertial measurement units (IMUs) and ranging sensors such as ultra-wideband radios (UWBs) are lightweight and low-cost
elements.2211.03093_8516b9322edc894065d34719b342b: Hence, range-inertial odomotry (RIO) with UWBs and IMUs is practically significant for flying robots
elements.2211.03093_d730f8f4dca98474acc7113d52628: More attractively, these sensors are omnidirectional and insusceptible to illumination conditions
elements.2211.03093_be6beb090d30276feb66d76aac7b9: The inconvenience is that multiple pre-installed and calibrated anchors are commonly required
elements.2211.03093_8993ffec75534e5292843e5f827d6: This hinders autonomous navigation in unknown environments
elements.2211.03093_763d13cf829ef3e8ee40b4a3111e3: To tackle this issue, previous researchers attempt to develop localization algorithms using a single UWB anchor
elements.2211.03093_f761a5caf5461da78243d7310e385: , which is referred as a single-ranging problem in this work
elements.2211.03093_4e6938d829891c6a143f40f19ea19: As such algorithms only need to fuse an IMU with a single UWB ranging measurement, pre-installation and calibration of anchors are no longer required
elements.2211.03093_4f62049718329691079ec801223bb: However, only using the IMU and UWB range measurements at a single time instance is insufficient to determine the position of a robot, and a sliding windows filtering (SWF) associated with observability analyses are necessary
elements.2211.03093_2493015c8e2a0b2bb4d03cada95eb: Such analyses are originated in the field of autonomous underwater vehicles
elements.2211.03093_a569b2bd268e2e4ef9aa467337307: , and the results are seamlessly applied for flying robots
elements.2211.03093_dbeb76859d93548465e6bb4d99eb0: Typically, the vehicles or robots are modeled as double-integral systems, and corresponding observability matrices are evaluated either linearly or nonlinearly
elements.2211.03093_34e3c259105245d21b4f6f7c5efea: These works commonly conclude that the observability is guaranteed only when accumulating actuation in arbitrary two axes is not constant or linearly dependent on each other
elements.2211.03093_868a4173d890044f90743012a2809: Regarding this conclusion, previous researchers attempt to enhance the observability and positioning performance with two approaches
elements.2211.03093_42eab52cb9c90b238981be5531099: The first one delicately designs controllers to guarantee linearly independent motions in different axes
elements.2211.03093_5570fc34c20830c50428792f107f9: The second one performs SWF along with observability evaluation
elements.2211.03093_a8453a685b7fafe8cd535fab977ce: As the first approach requires additional control efforts to guarantee positioning performance, this work focuses on the second one
elements.2211.03093_eb0eaa9016da02d36df360ca4a95d: Existing SWF approaches are commonly nonlinear, and their computational complexity is hyperlinear
elements.2211.03093_2ce4a0d9543923ba0af0f054f2664: Therefore, the sliding window cannot be too long
elements.2211.03093_ca5b91e500b167f0c6089309c7f37: Unfortunately, a short sliding window may only include small actuation in all the axes, which causes the observability matrix to be ill-conditioned, not to mention the observability itself is not theoretically guaranteed, as discussed already
elements.2211.03093_c45947666a073a529d86dbe2ea7c1: tries to perform a key-node selection approach to ehance the observability in an expanded long sliding window
elements.2211.03093_41a74fd2fa8055fa3c126600831a2: This approach is practically significant, but there are still two aspects requiring further investigation
elements.2211.03093_0af31eea7cde673598d246d201975: First, compared to previous research, there is no difference in the observability condition
elements.2211.03093_a567dba10476c43c8f13b8c3272d5: Therefore, it has to repeatedly compute the observability matrices and their inverse to find proper key nodes, which could be time-consuming
elements.2211.03093_6386bb281c6f45e24d0acceb1fa04: Second, the key-node selection is inherently a desampling and has unavoidable information loss
elements.2211.03093_e019f312bb056581d7e05e25bba41: Therefore, it is still necessary to further pursue a computationally efficient and observability guaranteed estimation approach for real-world application
elements.2211.03093_fe1a5fa0ee354cbb89202624e6ae3: In view of the state-of-the-art, we propose a framework of single-range and inertia based odometry (SRIBO) to enhance the observability with a refined model considering aerodynamics and improve its efficiency in long sling window with a dimension-reduced linear estimator
elements.2211.03093_11e45b79b55604a5a0e5fc7b085db: First, we refine the model of flying robots considering aerial drag effects, and the single-range inertial odometry (SRIO) merely using an IMU and a UWB is therewith formulated and proven to be observable almost surely
elements.2211.03093_c6dfe4faf7bf814516bcb39293781: In such a case, it is theoretically guaranteed that one can effectively estimate states taking measurements in an arbitrary horizon
elements.2211.03093_1cf4800b25c9b7f98e0eea5f42020: Subsequently, a dimension-reduced wriggling estimator (DWE) is proposed
elements.2211.03093_7abb3237191839d3345ae93c90602: This estimator slides the estimation horizon in a stepping manner, and output matrices are approximately evaluated based on a sequence of historical estimations
elements.2211.03093_77fae8d04fbeb65634da2c1f975c0: On this basis, we can formulate the optimal state estimation as a batched linear least-square programming
elements.2211.03093_e71f4d99545eddce8567e638fda97: Subsequently, a polynomial fitting approach is introduced to reduce the dimension as well as the computational complexity of the estimation
elements.2211.03093_7fb1e6cfd6cb5b93f1925d7556d1f: In this manner, the SRIO can estimate states in a sufficiently long interval with redundant measurements, which further improves the robustness of the estimation
elements.2211.03093_dfca1dc2e9fb25fb3206197e78661: The SRIO is also demonstrated to able to fuse with an additional optical flow sensor, and a so-called single-range, inertia, and optical-flow odometry (SRIFO) is performed
elements.2211.03093_009c5a633f2c3568e22e246ba55fd: The optical flow sensor provides additional velocity measurements to enhance the estimation performance further, yet failures of such measurements will not lead to singular solutions
elements.2211.03093_ba4094c30fa603ba9b718976047fc: Theoretically, both the SRIO and SRIFO in our SRIBO framework are proven to be numerically stable, asymptotic converging and fault-tolerant to sensor failures
elements.2211.03093_bf061574adeb98a6c02924b3002d9: Real-time experiments are conducted at last to verify the declarations of observability, computational efficiency, and resilience
elements.2211.03093_912fb3551583c5ec9e01eb083d600: The main contributions are two aspects: 1) modeling with aerial drag effects, the flying robot positioning with SRIBO algorithms is first formulated to be observable almost surely; 2) owing to its efficiency and resilience, the proposed linear DWE can perform estimation in a sufficiently long interval with redundant measurements, which enhances the degree of observability as well as the estimation performance.

elements.2211.03093_07f3a36bd5beeaac9477e8235986c: Nonetheless, the refined model considering aerial drag effects is still significant
elements.2211.03093_67bbbdc805a9fe8b18876d08fd5db: , when the aerial drag effects are excluded in the model, the positioning performance deteriorates even more significantly than that in the indoor environment
elements.2211.03093_4453b7aed97b2ef05650e499023b6: The performance of the SRIFO in the outdoor environment is also re-evaluated
elements.2211.03093_0b4e3af936e01ac41761e0655392b: The estimation results are demonstrated in Table
elements.2211.03093_f3ffb56fb6fea981e300f68d18669: The precision is similar to that in the indoor environment
elements.2211.03093_f8350063e27ecd081561bdf2a41eb: Meanwhile, the performance is also different when using different datasets, which is probably affected by the varying performance of the optical flow sensor
elements.2211.03093_ac4cafd7bc84467656725c108c6a0: Although we find slightly different results between the indoor and outdoor environments, the effectiveness of the proposed SRIBO is well proven with the aforementioned tests
elements.2211.03093_b0c60f072adfd1a4c6f7a838270c6: This implies the SRIBO can be used for indoor and outdoor positioning with various moving ranges.
elements.2211.03093_592729a211139d55c29b00e1f12e4: In this work, an efficient and resilient SRIBO framework using lightweight sensors is proposed for flying robots
elements.2211.03093_2a48aefc222bccd521e4da25ac650: Within this framework, one can perform the SRIO only using an IMU and a UWB
elements.2211.03093_930cdf82ba69f655fdca182c13b17: If an optical flow is available, an SRIFO can be further implemented for state estimation with even higher precision
elements.2211.03093_c248dfd2541c6d21d03e8fa1c0b94: The effectiveness of the proposed framework lies on two bases
elements.2211.03093_b1fd8e16104f6b68f0947001d8195: First, considering aerial drag effects, the SRIBO is formulated and proven to be locally weakly observable almost surely in real-world flight, and this conclusion significantly differs from existing works
elements.2211.03093_6428bf4d4254b524b4c570aad2879: Second, the linear and dimension-reduced SRIBO is able to estimate state in a sufficiently long interval with redundant measurements, which further enhances the degree of observability as well the estimation performance
elements.2211.03093_64905384c1db9b91e8f96ece84582: The convergence and numeric stability are also thoroughly investigated
elements.2211.03093_6f35f7fc046c1e3dd7d1b734649c1: Extensive experiments are carried out at last
elements.2211.03093_8d8e318033d56611443f97ac5a3f3: It is verified the observability is effectively enhanced by considering drag effects
elements.2211.03093_8261c8aab6523ca23ec3f54fb5f78: The SRIBO is also proven to be resilient to sensor failures and fault initialization
elements.2211.03093_4534884faf5c3bbc8d72550a142ca: The overall estimation precision and computational efficiency significantly outperform the state-of-the-art approaches, and it meets the requirements of real-world applications of autonomous navigation and the relative localization of multiple agents
elements.2211.03093_e832e8e8c06aedb6aa53192cb79e2: This framework can also be transferred to enhance the performance of the single-range based odometry for ground or underwater robots, because friction or drags also exists in those robots
elements.2211.03093_307a3f06271814b151f95aaefb4c1: One main limitation of this work is that the covariance matrices are set empirically, which hinders the approximation of global optimization
elements.2211.03093_d1c952ac5097244627d23b1bea487: In the future, we will try our best to improve the performance of the SRIBO regarding this aspect
elements.2211.03093_cc3973c353f94c68afa4ca2782a68: In addition, external disturbances, such as wind disturbances, are also worth compensating for a further improvement of the positioning performance.
